On Sat, 22 Nov 2003, Sage Green wrote:

> also, same question for the exhaust gaskets on the '72.

Loctite 518 on the exhaust gaskets. It is sticky, keeps them in place and
gives a perfect seal also. Don't use very much.

518 is rated only to 300F, but it works really well anyway.

